<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạntạsẖ wḥdạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qwm nzl ʿwdk .. mn ʿ ạlṣfṣạf
 wạstl nsẖydk .. zy ạlsyạf
 qwm rnm tạny .. mạntạsẖ wḥdạny
 dh ạlrb snydk .. wạlʿdw kẖwạf
 ạlqrạr- qwm rnm .. qwm rnm
 ạlrb yrdk .. wạlrysẖẗ fy ydk
 fwq ạlạ̉wtạr .. zy ạlmjdạf
 2- mrkbnạ ạtḥrk .. wạlmynạ ạtsẖạf
 wạlrys jnbk .. mạsk ạlkẖṭạf
 ạlbr ạlạ̉mạn .. ṭwl mạ ạlạ̹ymạn
 ngẖmạth fy qlbk .. ʿạlyyn wnḍạf
 3- qwm dh ạ̹lhk ḥy .. qạm mn byn ạlạ̉mwạt
 ạnfḍ kfn ạlạ̉ḥzạn .. qwm sydk qạm
 4- rạjʿ bgẖnạym .. lwly wạ̉ṣdạf
 wạlmrkb ʿạym .. mn kẖyr ạ̉ṣnạf
 ʿmạl btrtl .. ʿwdk byhll
 frḥk yạ smạwy .. mạlhwsẖ ạ̉wṣạf</lyrics>
